            "$\\frac{a_{1}}{1 - q} = 1$，$\\frac{|a_{1}|}{1 - |q|} = 2$",
            "由前一式知 $a_{1} > 0$，进而 $1 - q = 2(1 - |q|) = 2(1 + q)$，得 $q = -\\frac{1}{3}$",
            "则 $a_{1} = 1 - q = \\frac{4}{3}$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["$\\frac{4}{3}$"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "Expression",
