        "context": "2022年全国高中数学联合竞赛A2卷一试",
        "question": "在平面直角坐标系中，$F_{1}$、$F_{2}$ 分别为双曲线 $\\Omega: x^{2} - \\frac{y^{2}}{3} = 1$ 的左、右焦点，过 $F_{1}$ 的直线 $l$ 交 $\\Omega$ 于两点 $P, Q$。若 $\\overrightarrow{F_{1}F_{2}} \\cdot \\overrightarrow{F_{1}P} = 16$，则 $\\overrightarrow{F_{2}P} \\cdot \\overrightarrow{F_{2}Q}$ 的值为______。",
        "solution": [
            "由条件知 $F_{1}(-2, 0)$，$F_{2}(2, 0)$",
            "设 $P(x_{1}, y_{1})$，$Q(x_{2}, y_{2})$，由 $\\overrightarrow{F_{1}F_{2}} \\cdot \\overrightarrow{F_{1}P} = 16$ 知 $4(x_{1} + 2) + 0 \\cdot y_{1} = 16$",
            "故 $x_{1} = 2$，进而 $y_{1}^{2} = 3(x_{1}^{2} - 1) = 9$",
            "由对称性，不妨设 $y_{1} = 3$，则直线 $l$ 的方程为 $x = \\frac{4}{3}y - 2$",
            "代入 $\\Omega$ 的方程，消去 $x$ 并化简可得 $y$ 的二次方程 $13y^{2} - 48y + 27 = 0$",
            "其两根 $y_{1}, y_{2}$ 之积为 $\\frac{27}{13}$",
            "因此 $\\overrightarrow{F_{2}P} \\cdot \\overrightarrow{F_{2}Q} = (x_{1} - 2)(x_{2} - 2) + y_{1}y_{2} = 0 + \\frac{27}{13} = \\frac{27}{13}$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["$\\frac{27}{13}$"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "Expression",
        "error": null
    },
